name: Console-tdm
tagline: Console display manager based on CDM
body:
This program is a session selector written in bash, with similar functionnalities to CDM.

This is a fork of the TDM display manager program by [mytbk](https://github.com/mytbk).
The original source can be found [here](https://github.com/mytbk/console-tdm).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
